<h2 id="split-tp-sl"> Split TP and SL </h2>

<p><code>POST /v2/order/split-tp-sl</code></p>

<p>Add split TP/SL to a specific position. It requires a unique position ID, along with the quantity and price for TP and SL respectively. This operation enables dividing take-profit and stop-loss levels across multiple targets, helping optimize risk management and profit-taking for the position.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code><span class="k">async</span> <span class="kd">function</span> <span class="nx">split_tp_sl</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="c1">// Define the API endpoint for adding margin</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">endpoint</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">/v2/order/split-tp-sl</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">;</span>

    <span class="c1">// Define the fixed values for positionId and amount</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">positionId</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">"</span><span class="s2">18c6c979-b089-4e67-b627-4c2072d0d5cb</span><span class="dl">"</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// Unique identifier for the position</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">tp_quantity</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.01</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// Quantity of TP</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">tp_price</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">95000</span> <span class="c1">// Price of TP</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">sl_quantity</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mf">0.01</span><span class="p">;</span>  <span class="c1">// Quantity of SL</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">sl_price</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">85000</span> <span class="c1">// Price of SL   </span>

    <span class="c1">// Prepare request payload</span>
    <span class="kd">const</span> <span class="nx">params</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
        <span class="na">positionId</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">positionId</span><span class="p">,</span>  <span class="c1">// ID of the position to which margin is being added</span>
        <span class="na">splitTakeProfitOrders</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[{</span> <span class="c1">// Take Profit quantity and price</span>
          <span class="na">quantity</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">tp_quantity</span><span class="p">,</span>
          <span class="na">price</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">tp_price</span>
        <span class="p">}],</span>
        <span class="na">splitStopLossOrders</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="p">[{</span> <span class="c1">// Stop Loss quantity and price</span>
          <span class="na">quantity</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">sl_quantity</span><span class="p">,</span>
          <span class="na">price</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="nx">sl_price</span>
        <span class="p">}],</span>

    <span class="p">};</span>

    <span class="c1">// Call the postRequest function to send the POST request to the API</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="k">await</span> <span class="nx">postRequest</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">endpoint</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">params</span><span class="p">);</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">split_tp_sl</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">position_id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Enter the positionId: "</span><span class="p">)</span>
